                                        </div>
                                        <div id="source-statistics-nz." class="section level5 unlisted unnumbered hasAnchor">
                                            <h5>Source: Statistics NZ.<a href="https://6229.freelancedeveloper.site/introduction#source-statistics-nz." class="anchor-section" aria-label="Anchor link to header"></a></h5>
